	<ul>
		<li><%= "<b>Borrower survey:</b> #{link_to 'Click here', 'https://docs.google.com/forms/d/116rkhbOiafYI82lBesl-3v9LB1iIYah2rv_D8Y_rz4Q/viewform?usp=send_form', id: 'borrower_survey' }".html_safe %></li>
		<li><%= "<b>Lender survey:</b> #{link_to 'Click here', 'https://docs.google.com/forms/d/17znNQgaU7HaJEqxoHgzo16yEMy4DDH8gr4OEG1tlUEU/viewform?usp=send_form', id: 'lender_survey' }".html_safe %></li>
	</ul>

<p>Thank you, hope you'll use Project Borrow again!</p>

<p>James</p>

<p><a href="http://www.projectborrow.com/?utm_source=james%40projectborrow&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=email%20signature">Click here</a> to borrow something. Please feel free to share with your friends!</p>

</body> 
